{
  "stem": "21626.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My sister, of course, had stayed, and was, by then, working as a midwife in London.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I had a bit of a problem before I left, because the Ministry of Defense decided they wanted me to spy for them in England.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, unfortunately, had I said no, they would never have let me leave, because I knew too much.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I was trained as a spy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But of course, I had no intention of working for them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They wanted me to work on the routes that peop-- the escape routes prominent people were using, you know, to flee from Czechoslovakia to Britain.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I had to be in London.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I had to remain single.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I'm-- so that I would be a free agent, they say, couldn't be help to them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they made this perfectly clear.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So obviously, the minute I arrived, I went as far from London as I could to Liverpool and entered Miss [?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Fawkes ?] Secretarial College to learn to be a secretary, so that I could earn my living and again, obviously, was with the Rainfords and my other friends there, though I stayed more or less independent.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But then they started writing to me-- we had a special code with Ministry of Defense-- and threatening me that if I did not play ball, my aunt would suffer.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So you can understand what predicament I was in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So eventually, I had to go to London, at least please them in that respect.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I got a job there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I kept sending them things which I knew were absolutely useless and unimportant.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they kept getting so cross.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they said, you're an intelligent woman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, what you-- what sort of a game are you playing with us?",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
